{"tid":1853162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Kelly Online】內地民眾奇招自救 自製柚子皮口罩防疫","createTime":"2020-01-30T20:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T23:52:29.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"193ba79968c82b81ade3760c6a1790e90e7b2603","tid":1853162,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T20:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013015442139667.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013015442139667.jpg&h=2db54de1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n內地民眾利用柚子皮充當口罩。網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n全球各地口罩搶購競爭激烈，不但有人利用蒸餾水樽當頭罩預防飛沫，更有立法會議員教人蒸熱口罩重用聲稱「實是沒有辦法中辦法，總比不戴口罩上街或不作消毒而重複使用好」。內地有民眾更創意「爆燈」，利用柚子皮當口罩。<br />\n<br />\n有內地民眾在頭部罩上一個塑膠水桶，或是自製膠樽面罩及呼吸防護器，深怕飛沫病毒跑進自己的臉部和眼睛中，分分鐘可能比口罩更有效；另外也有人頭戴全罩式頭盔，或是全身套住塑膠袋，以求自保，不過最奇特的是有內地民眾利用柚子皮自製成口罩，在大街和地鐵中都能見到戴著柚子皮口罩的人，都可謂十分「環保」，還可以陣陣柚子飄香。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013015442385838.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013015442385838.jpg&h=bb1fa933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013015530386745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013015530386745.jpg&h=f895b681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民稱，「好笑歸好笑，但悲劇正是此，農村不僅買不起口罩，而且也買不到口罩了，許多老人家為了自保，只好用柚子皮代替，至少有心理上的安慰」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013015474095261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013015474095261.jpg&h=363566f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013015442215395.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013015442215395.jpg&h=0deb2e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過若認真要防止被病毒感染，民眾還是需配戴N95口罩或醫療用口罩，並經常洗手消毒，才能真的達到自保的效果。"},{"pid":"eb8134cba6bb0a309b889638b1448b22a28031d7","tid":1853162,"uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T20:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013015442475884.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013015442475884.jpg&h=6102bb88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013015442313024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013015442313024.jpg&h=9d001819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013015442599291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013015442599291.jpg&h=1706a93a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013022595728169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013022595728169.jpg&h=dd92e0ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013022595980160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200130%2F_2020013022595980160.jpg&h=68cffe13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200130/_2020013023000047827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://